  "prompt": "How do you politely turn down someone who wants to \"grab coffee sometime\"?",
  "response": "Politely declining an invitation to grab coffee can be done graciously by expressing gratitude for the offer and clarifying your current situation or constraints. Here\u2019s how you might respond:\n\n\"Thank you so much for the invitation to grab coffee. I appreciate it, but I'm currently managing a pretty busy schedule. Let's definitely keep in touch, though, and perhaps we can connect in the future!\"\n\nThis response shows appreciation for their offer while being clear about your inability to meet at this time.",
